形成一层保护膜</view><view class="text_sc data-v-002b67d2">所以如果你先用霜状的产品，它已经在皮肤表层形成了一层保护膜，你再用水，用精华等小分子的产品，这些小分子便无法渗透进皮肤到达深层去发挥功效。很多女孩子真的以为抹了就万事大吉了，不管步骤。</view></view></block><block wx:if="{{haveItem==''}}"><image class="img data-v-002b67d2" src="../../static/img/kcw.jpg" mode="widthFix"></image></block></view></block><block wx:if="{{tabSel==1}}"><view class="scl_content data-v-002b67d2"><image class="img data-v-002b67d2" src="../../static/img/kcjs.png" mode="widthFix"></image></view></block><view class="but_bot_btn data-v-002b67d2"><block wx:if="{{haveItem==''}}"><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['buyBtn',['$event']]]]]}}" class="btn blue lg data-v-002b67d2" bindtap="__e">立即购买</button></block></view><uni-popup vue-id="f02b7f9a-1" type="bottom" data-ref="showshare" class="data-v-002b67d2 vue-ref" bind:__l="__l" vue-slots="{{['default']}}"><view class="share_to_popup_body data-v-002b67d2"><view class="title data-v-002b67d2">分享到</view><view class="imgs data-v-002b67d2"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['shareTo',['wx']]]]]}}" class="item data-v-002b67d2" bindtap="__e"><image class="img data-v-002b67d2" src="../../static/img/weix.png"></image></view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['shareTo',['pyq']]]]]}}" class="item data-v-002b67d2" bindtap="__e"><image class="img data-v-002b67d2" src="../../static/img/pengyq.png"></image></view></view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['closePopup',['share']]]]]}}" class="close_popup iconfont iconguanbi data-v-002b67d2" bindtap="__e"></view></view></uni-popup><uni-popup vue-id="f02b7f9a-2" type="bottom" data-ref="orderPay" class="data-v-002b67d2 vue-ref" bind:__l="__l" vue-slots="{{['default']}}"><view class="order_pay_popup data-v-002b67d2"><view class="p1 red data-v-002b67d2">￥160.00</view><view class="p2 data-v-002b67d2">商品购买</view><radio-group data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['RadioChange',['$event']]]]]}}" class="block data-v-002b67d2" bindchange="__e"><view class="cu-form-group_sy data-v-002b67d2"><view class="item data-v-002b67d2